The 2010 census reported 247 people and 92 housing units in the CDP. The 2010 census reported [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|racial makeup]] was 88.7% White, 0.4% American Indian and Alaska Native, and 10.9% other races. Hispanic or Latino heritage comprised 19.0% of the population.<ref name="census2">{{cite web |title=U.S. Census website |url=https://www.census.gov |accessdate=May 23, 2011 |publisher=[[United States Census Bureau]]}}</ref>

